Title: Caltech Archetypes/eText Project
Body: Date: Wed, 20 Nov 1996 19:12:01 GMT Server: Apache/1.1.1 Content-type: text/html Content-length: 4054 Last-modified: Sun, 15 Sep 1996 03:12:28 GMT Caltech Archetypes/eText Project The Caltech Archetypes / eText Project The Caltech Archetypes/eText project combines work in two areas: an investigation of programming archetypes , where a programming archetype (briefly) is an abstraction from a class of programs with a common structure and includes class-specific design strategies and a collection of example program designs and implementations.
